# Note: Firebase web config (apiKey, etc.) is NOT a secret — those values are
# meant to identify the Firebase project from a browser and are visible to any
# visitor anyway. Security comes from Firestore/Storage Rules and Auth.
# So we COMMIT firebase-config.js. If you change your mind, uncomment the line:
# assets/js/firebase-config.js

